<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on July 14, issued by China
's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 26 degrees C., max. 37 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 25 degrees C., max. 31 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 26 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 5 degrees C., max. 15 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
