Stock Exchange ended higher Thursday due to the peso recovery.
</P>
<P>
The 30-company Phisix, the market's main index, closed 6.95
points higher at 1561.52.
</P>
<P>
But, the broader all-shares index closed marginally lower by 10
of a point at 666.69.
</P>
