<TEXT>
<P>
YINCHUAN, July 13 (Xinhua) -- The tourism industry in northwest
China's Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region has got a boost with the
holding of the five-day Yellow River International Tourism
Festival, tourism officials said today.
</P>
<P>
