personnel in the military police, but currently, the number has
risen to 7,110, said Sao Sokha, head of the military police.
</P>
<P>
Military police have been trained on various respects of
professionalism, including military skills, knowledge of laws and
democracy as well as human rights.
</P>
<P>
Military police have been seen as one of the most competent
authorities to protect social order, especially to fight against
crimes in this country. 
