The 17 Lao were among a group who clashed with Lao government
forces at the Vang Tao border checkpoint on July 3 and fled across
the Thai-Lao border with 11 Thais.
</P>
<P>
The 28 men were detained by Thai authorities in the Ubon
Rachathani Province, 695 kilometers northeast of Bangkok.
</P>
<P>
