computer and information technology sectors up more then 3.8
percent.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt's Xetra Dax ended up firmly as tech stocks followed a
buoyant Nasdaq index higher amid signs the sector's slump since
early March was ending. The index closed up 130.02 or 1.84 percent
at 7195.99 points.
</P>
