<HEADLINE> Sao Paulo Stocks Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Stocks on the Sao Paulo
Securities Exchange, the largest in Latin America, closed down
Thursday with the key Bovespa Index falling by 3.57 percent to 16,
